content: Landed in NYC. Not the same Xavier anymore. Japan changed me. Ready for what's next.
raw_content:
**Major Events and Changes Tweet:**

"Touchdown in NYC after an unforgettable journey through Japan. The skyscrapers of Tokyo have given way to the familiar skyline of home, but I'm not the same Xavier who left. This trip has reshaped my views on culture, technology, and myself. Excited yet uncertain, ready to blend my experiences into my next chapter. #Homecoming #LifeLessons #PersonalGrowth"
